{"tid":166862,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（放底心事）你一直都係當我好朋友。","createTime":"2017-03-22T12:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T12:53:03.000Z","uid":33221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49cb183ba877a12ff70e941836c0c1e07000c5be","tid":166862,"uid":33221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:22:21.000Z","msg":"一齊放底心事，等自己舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我先<br />\n<br />\n<del>------------------------------------------<br />\n</del><br />\n我知道嫁啦，之後都問過你喜不喜歡我，但你話冇、諗下先，我講過鐘意你，你都冇任何表示，你表示過嘅就係你鐘意的高富帥。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我叫過你加油追男神，但其實自己都好唔開心，你一定一定唔會知。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後失敗又係我氹吓你。<br />\n<br />\n問題點解你唔鐘意我仲要同我傾計秒回我，其實我仲有冇機會，唔想再食檸檬呀！我放棄其他女仔就係等緊你，我會等到你有男朋友先死心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又等唔等到呢？"},{"pid":"6788c1e5a01e72d692738b1ea17b247be8d93d84","tid":166862,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:26:57.000Z","msg":"bff"},{"pid":"3d3fffb9200c52d6a238ca5fb8f2e9139a052a00","tid":166862,"uid":33221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:30:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>bff</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a407470b18f7479e07ca3de6e7e6647e06e682","tid":166862,"uid":33221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:53:03.000Z","msg":"朋友，我當你一世朋友"}]}